This class contains a series of methods used to create a log text (that will be saved through an Acceleo template into a file).

initLog

public static void initLog(boolean createLog,
                           boolean logDebugText,
                           boolean printToConsole,
                           boolean saveToFile,
                           java.lang.String modelName)
Configures the necessary variables. Called from Acceleo's marte2mast.mtl template.

Parameters:
createLog - true if you want the log text to be created, false if not Not sure if it's used anymore.
logDebugText - true if you want the debug text (created using debugPrintln) to be stored, false if not
printToConsole - true if you want to print the text to the console (using System.out.print...), false if not
saveToFile - true if you want the log text to be saved into a file, false if not
modelName - the name of the Model (used to generate the name of the log file)
